emuInput.TitMainTitle: George Mason, David Washington, Jessie Vann, Mrs. McKinley King receiving gift of appreciation, and Daisy Lampkin, during annual Alpha Phi Alpha picnic, North Park
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 27, 1946, pg. 14 reads: "Honor Prexy's Wife - Alpha Omicron Lambda Chapter of Alpha Phi Alpha Fraternity gave a special gift of appreciation to Mrs. McKinley King, wife of the fraternity president, at the annual picnic last Friday at North Park. On th photo (left to right) are :George Mason, emcee; David Washington, MRs. Robert L .Vann, Mrs. King and Mrs. Daisy Lampkin. - Harris Photo."
